WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.501 --> 00:00:03.069
I woke up not so early because

00:00:04.437 --> 00:00:07.273
because I wanted to enjoy sunrise
on top of Baigu.

00:00:07.640 --> 00:00:08.608
It was stunning.

00:00:09.509 --> 00:00:11.911
I was prepared for snow or wet bamboo,

00:00:12.045 --> 00:00:13.546
but the weather was perfect.

00:00:13.913 --> 00:00:15.782
I carried all my water from Guguan

00:00:15.882 --> 00:00:18.451
and still had enough for the night and morning.

00:00:18.752 --> 00:00:19.753
Clear sky,

00:00:20.019 --> 00:00:21.521
but it was getting late.

00:00:21.955 --> 00:00:24.891
I decided to sleep on top of Baigu Mountain.

00:00:27.060 --> 00:00:28.528
Bai Gu Da Shan

00:00:29.095 --> 00:00:31.364
I don't like spending money
on gear I don't need,

00:00:31.631 --> 00:00:34.567
but years ago I invested in good sleep gear.

00:00:34.934 --> 00:00:38.338
My whole sleep system
weighs under 1,200 grams.

00:00:39.472 --> 00:00:41.307
Good 20F down sleeping bag,

00:00:41.608 --> 00:00:45.111
short inflatable mat, quality bivy and tarp.

00:00:45.612 --> 00:00:48.448
I don't recommend sleeping
on top of mountain or open space.

00:00:48.715 --> 00:00:51.351
It's always better to sleep
under some vegetation.

00:00:51.985 --> 00:00:52.719
But if you do, 

00:00:52.719 --> 00:00:54.721
you have to have good weather and know

00:00:54.821 --> 00:00:57.157
what to do if something is turning wrong.

00:00:57.457 --> 00:00:58.758
I slept well.

